title: Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston
text:
> Sports Yankees clinch playoff spot after 2-year absence, top Boston New York Yankees Carlos Beltran, right, points skyward as he crosses the plate after hitting a second-inning, solo, home run off Boston Red Sox starting pitcher Rich Hill in a baseball game in New York, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015. Red Sox catcher Sandy Leon is at left. (AP Photo/Kathy Willens)
